IDEAS
----------------------
Following is a random list of ideas that could be implemented:

 * Weather Generator - given climate / time of year / etc
 * Calendar - create custom calendar / track time withing the campaign
 * Town Generator/settelment - create towns / villages / etc.. with population - including (warriors, monks, towns gaurd, etc)
 * Treasure Generator
 * Random Dungeon Generator
 * Time Tracker -- Game clock keeps in game time. Advances after each round or if dm pushes it forward x hours
 * Power Tracker -- Keep track of used and expended powers during an encounter
 * Campaign Diary
 * Encounter Generator -- Generate Enconunters base on some form of template or random




